        "timestamp": "2018-03-22 23:46:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\nDileep, got it. I might add that in another patch as it's not fetchable through extra specs and will need it's own flow to the best of my knowledge.",
        "patchset_number": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "bea36155ba9f6ae0306c85c764a444216a7c0047",
        "author": {
