          "email": "Nathaniel.Potter@intel.com",
          "username": "ntpttr"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-03-22 23:48:15.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\n@Dileep, in fact I think that instruction set extensions is exposed through the traits API, which is out of scope for this newton file and will need to be added in Ocata alongside the changes Haibin has made there.",
